==French==
===Adjective===

# [[Brown]] (in colour); ''marron pourpré'' ("purplish brown") is the English [[maroon]] colour.
# Caught, done for, loser.
# One who illegally exercises a profession, or has doubtful or illicit practices. ''Magie marronne'': Hedge magic.

===Noun===

# The [[chestnut]], a large edible fruit.
# The [[horse-chestnut]], a non-edible fruit.
# A [[maroon]], a slave or animal who has run away to live free.
# A token used as a control of the presence of someone at his post.
# In [[pyrotechnics]], the [[maroon]], a firecracker on a rocket.
# In popular speech, a fist punch.
# In popular speech, the head.

